TV Magazine testing times Jeremy McConnell takes paternity test to see if he is father of Stephanie Davis’ son live on This Morning – and the results will be processed in Jeremy Kyle’s lab 
Former Celebrity Big Brother star appeared on This Morning on Wednesday to discuss his ongoing paternity battle with his ex By JILL ROBINSON, SHOWBIZ REPORTER 8th February 2017, 9:17 am
